data.title: Rufus King (band)
data.meta_description: Rufus King is an alternative rock band from Woodland, CA. They wrote and performed the song, "Just What I Need", which is featured in the film Bring It On.
data.text:
Rufus King is an alternative rock band from Woodland, CA. They wrote and performed the song, "Just What I Need",[1] which is featured in the film Bring It On.[2]
